image.altText: A concrete footpath overgrown with weeds outside newly constructed houses.

props.synopsis: It is a federal housing scheme designed to transform the lives of the profoundly disabled. But a Four Corners investigation has found more than 1,000 of these purpose-built homes are sitting empty.

image.altText: A screen showing stock markets results, as seen through a window.

image.altText: A split image of a Ford Ranger PHEV, with the front half outside and the back half charging in a garage.
